plugin: manual
id: gnome-text-editor
flags: simple
_description:
 PURPOSE:
       Check that gnome-text-editor runs and works correctly
 STEPS:
      1. Run gnome-text-editor from the desktop icon. Does the icon look correct?
      2. Make sure hamburger menu -> Help brings up the Help page
      3. Type and save a document. Relaunch and make sure you can open it or another document
      4. Open a new tab
      5. Try some different settings available with the wheel icon

unit: test plan
id: gnome-text-editor-tp
name: gnome-text-editor test plan
include: gnome-text-editor
